-- The antisym/trans/total fields are marked to be replaced with case-split
-- proofs — the DEPTH RESULT is exactly how many of them the current surface can
-- express as proofs (zero-delta) vs still need Axiom. Contrast the stub arm,
-- where ALL four are Axiom by choice. Discriminator: the trusted_base delta.
